<template>
    <button class="buttonDef">{{name}}</button>
</template>

<script>


export default {
    props:
    {
        name:
        {
            type: String,
            default: "NONE"
        },
    }
}
</script>

<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Varela+Round&display=swap');
    .buttonDef{
        font-family: Varela Round;
        background: #FF387A;
        color: #FBE5ED;
        padding: 6px 24px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    } 
</style>
